<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1437,151,968]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,591,439,464]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
Measurements of 
<typeStatus box="[416,525,440,464]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Holotype</typeStatus>
male
</emphasis>
. Distended body length 1200. Head length 103 (length including anterior prolongation 107), width across cheeks 140; compound eye dorsal length 58, width 43. Pronotal median length 115, width 175; posteroangular setae I length 70–96, setae II length 88–90; posteromarginal setae I length 35. Metascutal median length 70, median setae length 43–45. Fore wings length 630, width at middle 40?. Antennal segments I to VII length (width) as follows: 28 (30), 35 (26), 48 (19), 45 (19), 31 (19), 53 (20), 15 (8).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1437,151,968]" box="[151,366,620,644]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
